{
  "id": "adv_event_2110_01_01",
  "title": "誕生日前夜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロが東京に進出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One night‚ a while after Hoshimi Productions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しばらく経ったある日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "moved to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "endTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokohroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すぅ……すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.966666666666667,
      "endTime": 14.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokohroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……麻奈か？\n久しぶりだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana… Are you Mana?\nIt’s been a while…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.033333333333333,
      "endTime": 20.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？　何か言ってくれ\nまた、あの頃みたいに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter? Say something.\nJust like that time‚ again—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 26.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokohroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　……夢か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… It was a dream…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 32.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "夢で麻奈に会うのはめずらしいな\n一体なんで……あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s rare seeing Mana in my dreams.\nWhy now…? Ahh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33,
      "endTime": 39.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、明日は麻奈の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Tomorrow is Mana’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 43.866666666666674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 45.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "明日は、お姉ちゃんの誕生日か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow’s my sister’s birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 49.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "またみんなで\n麻奈さんのバースデーパーティーやろうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s all of us throw a\nbirthday party for Mana-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 55.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 57.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……さくらはああ言ってくれたけど\nみんなを巻き込んじゃうのは申し訳ないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what Sakura said‚ but\nI feel bad about getting everybody involved in it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 64.47333323590391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "前はどんなお祝いをしてたんだろう？\n……そうだ、日記……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did we celebrate it before again?\nRight‚ the diary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 70.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 68.1
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 72.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "「2016年10月9日\n誕生日だー！！　忘れてたー！！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"October 9‚ 2016\"\n\"It's my birthday! I forgot!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1,
      "endTime": 80.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "「ライブ会場のコールで思い出したよ……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Hearing the celebrations at the live venue reminded me…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.26666666666667,
      "endTime": 84.36666661898295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "「普通アイドルの誕生日って\n生誕祭的なことをやるんじゃないのかな？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Don't idols usually have \"\n\"birthday events on their birthdays?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "endTime": 90.79999993064187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "「いつもどーりなライブだったし……もう！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I performed my live just as usual…Oh no…!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 95.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "「来年は！\n絶対にバースデーライブやるんだからっ！！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Next year!\"\n\"I'll definitely do a special birthday live!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 100.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 101.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "もう、{user}さんったら、酷いなあ\nお姉ちゃんのお誕生日、祝ってあげなかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was really bad of {user}-san.\nHe didn’t do anything to celebrate my sister’s birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "endTime": 110.93333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 111.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、私も同じか。ちゃんとお祝いして\nあげればよかったな。ごめんね、お姉ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But I’m just the same. I should have celebrated her\nbirthday properly. I’m sorry‚ Sis.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.26666666666667,
      "endTime": 122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "次の年は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s written for next year…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 124.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 126.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "「2017年10月9日\n念願のバースデーライブ！！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"October 9‚ 2017\"\n\"Finally~ It's the birthday live!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "「新曲お披露目やら特大ケーキ登場やら\nてんこ盛りな内容で……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"The show was full of many things‚ including the unveiling\"\n\"of a new song and the appearance of an oversized cake…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 141.20000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "「んー、一年待った甲斐があったよー！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Well‚ it was worth the one-year wait!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.66666666666666,
      "endTime": 145.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "「盛り上げてくれたファンの人たちにも\n三枝さんやマネージャーにも感謝、感謝です！！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"To the fans‚ Saegusa-san‚ and my manager‚\"\n\"who made it so much fun‚thank you all so much!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 152.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "「来年はもっとも～っと盛り上げたいなー\n今から楽しみ！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Next year I hope to make it even more exciting!\"\n\"I can't wait already!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5,
      "endTime": 160.13333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなと大勢でお祝いしたんだ……\nふふっ、お姉ちゃんらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She celebrated with a crowd of fans…\nHehe! That’s just like my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.16666666666666,
      "endTime": 170.59999999999997,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8300.000000000011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 170.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
